The paper evaluates the performance of mobile AI accelerators for deep learning models, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) research. The paper also discusses the deployment of deep learning models on mobile devices, which could fall under the categories of augmented reality (cs.AR), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), and multimedia (cs.MM).
